narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: yes. though i would like to take a book out for more than just one day.
An unfortunate amount of material seems to be floating and misplaced in the library system, hindering research and access to reading materials. I believe I will continue to be annoyed by this.
